#

Creamy Broccoli Cheddar Soup

30 min
$12.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

DairyOnion

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianComfort Food

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Soup

Tags:

SoupCheesyEasy Meal

Description

A velvety and comforting soup packed with fresh broccoli and rich cheddar cheese, perfect for a cozy meal.

Ingredients

  • fresh broccoli florets: 2 cups
  • sharp cheddar cheese: 1 cup, shredded
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • heavy cream: 1 cup
  • onion: 1, diced
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • butter: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • nutmeg: a pinch
